      <title>[우리 아기가 태어났어요] 공혜지·박래민 딸 새봄 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/culture-life/culture_general/2025/11/28/6UOMBCBXFJE3JG5CA6NJVG3CJE/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/culture-life/culture_general/2025/11/28/6UOMBCBXFJE3JG5CA6NJVG3CJE/</guid>
